  "keyFeatures": [
    "Chain-of-Causation (CoC) reasoning for interpretable autonomous driving decisions",
    "Diffusion-based trajectory prediction over a 6.4s horizon at 10Hz (64 waypoints)",
    "Classifier-free guidance (CFG) with navigation conditioning for steerable trajectories",
    "Flexible multi-camera support (up to 7 cameras) with variable camera counts at inference",
    "Visual Question Answering (VQA) for scene understanding",
    "Reinforcement Learning post-training for reasoning-trajectory alignment",
    "Built on Qwen3-VL backbone with a 10B parameter scale"
  ],
